bgm.name: 探索15(セキュリティホール)

parameters:
\n<Female>Are you an adventurer? I haven't seen your face before. It's
better for your own good not to get too close to the
residential area. Unfamiliar faces are met with caution. You
should stop here.

\n<Female>It would be good for you to offer prayers at the church.
There might be some kind of divine protection for you. Not
that I know of, though.
Part of the wall seems suspicious... Let's try touching it.

A door appeared...! It looks like it was camouflaged with
sand and stones.
I don't want to enter here anymore.
It looks like a grave has been dug up...
It looks like a grave has been dug up...

There's alcohol offered here. I wonder if one would want to
drink even after death? I don't know...
